Mount Steele.jpg|5. [[Mount Steele]] in Yukon is the fifth-highest summit of Canada.
Fairweather.jpg|9. [[Mount Fairweather]] on the Alaska border is the highest summit of British Columbia.
Mount Waddington.jpg|19. [[Mount Waddington]] is the highest summit of the [[Coast Mountains]] of British Columbia.
Mt Robson South Face.jpg|21. [[Mount Robson]] in British Columbia is the highest summit of the [[Canadian Rockies]].
mtcolumbia.jpg|28. [[Mount Columbia (Canada)|Mount Columbia]] on the British Columbia border is the highest summit of Alberta.
MtSirSandfordbyTrevor.jpg|40. [[Mount Sir Sandford]] is the highest summit of the [[Sir Sandford Range]] of British Columbia.
Mt. Sir Wilfred Laurier.JPG|41. [[Mount Sir Wilfrid Laurier]] is the highest summit of the [[Cariboo Mountains]] of British Columbia.
